Now *CO* &gt; *EO*, since the sun is just above the horizon.

Therefore ∠ *PEQ* &gt; ∠ *FCG*.

And ∠ *PEQ* &gt; 1/200 *R* but &lt; 1/164 *R*, where *R* represents a
right angle.

