It follows that *d<sub>u</sub>* &lt; 10,000 *d<sub>e</sub>*.

\(2\) (Perimeter of earth) ≯ 3,000,000 stadia. \[Assumption 1\]

and (perimeter of earth) &gt; 3 *d<sub>e</sub>*.

Therefore *d<sub>e</sub>* &lt; 1,000,000 stadia,

